{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01CupDQGyjLzQGvUiRFaidg7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_015NrLtSxACtsf1SWsF7BGqz","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Review title-extractor changes","subagent_type":"code-review-expert","prompt":"Review the following changes made to `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts`. Focus on correctness, consistency, and whether the approach is sound.\n\n**Change 1: METADATA_PATTERNS addition (line ~77)**\n```typescript\n/^MAIN\\s+RECIPE\\s*:/i,    // \"MAIN RECIPE: ...\" structural prefix lines\n```\n\n**Change 2: passesHardFilters() addition (after bullet-list check, line ~322)**\n```typescript\n// Lines starting with \"--\" are sub-section headers (e.g., \"--VARIATION:\", \"--WERSJA NOWOCZESNA\")\nif (/^--\\s*\\w/.test(text)) return false;\n```\n\n**Change 3: Dedup logic guard (line ~1189)**\n```typescript\nselected = selected.filter((a) => {\n  const aLower = a.text.toLowerCase();\n  // Protect compound titles — these use explicit separators and the full form is intentional\n  if (/ [+:] /.test(a.text)) return true;\n  return !selected.some(\n    (b) =>\n      b !== a &&\n      aLower.includes(b.text.toLowerCase()) &&\n      b.text.length < a.text.length\n  );\n});\n```\n\n**Context:**\n- This file extracts recipe titles from OCR text\n- METADATA_PATTERNS filters out non-title lines early\n- passesHardFilters() is a hard gate before scoring\n- The dedup logic keeps the SHORTER candidate when one is a substring of another (this is intentional and must not be changed)\n- The compound title guard prevents ` : ` and ` + ` separated titles from being eliminated by the shorter-wins rule\n\nPlease check:\n1. Are the regex patterns correct and not over-broad?\n2. Is the `/ [+:] /` compound guard in the dedup potentially harmful for edge cases?\n3. Are there consistency issues — should the `--` pattern also be added to METADATA_PATTERNS instead of passesHardFilters?\n4. Any other concerns?\n\nRead the relevant sections of the file at `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts` for full context (lines 45-80, 306-350, 1184-1200)."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":392,"cache_read_input_tokens":31657,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":392},"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7a79a908-8d4c-4852-8920-c5c4df3c5fbb","uuid":"c86a03f9-9aea-4d87-bd30-45f03c37c96d"}
